{"tid":1013774,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"傳賭王何鴻燊入ICU 養和醫院門外多間傳媒守候","createTime":"2019-02-08T15:11:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-09T01:28:41.000Z","uid":2054,"like":43,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"ea58b38314e17a7165aa8360d7d611c28e9a5acb","tid":1013774,"uid":2054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T15:11:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190208&amp;s=7018882&amp;a=59238105\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190208%26s%3D7018882%26a%3D59238105&d=SInmTBH44R2CRaFL2yHJ1KDCEJE6krTJKQ6%2BfiBCJRk%3D&h=906364d7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190208%26s%3D7018882%26a%3D59238105&h=74e6d609\" target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190208&amp;s=7018882&amp;a=59238105</a><br />\n<br />\n今晚9點多，突然傳出賭王何鴻燊病況轉差消息，有指他轉入ICU，有不少傳媒在養和醫院門外守候。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，有傳媒拍到眾房子女來到醫院，當中包括甚少露面的大房長女何超賢、孫女何家華、二房何超鳳、三太陳婉珍及何超蓮，而四太梁安琪於晚上9點來到醫院，但她們都同一口徑否認賭王病情有變化，三太及四太還向傳媒派利是。《蘋果》聯絡四太，電話駁上call機，而超蓮就以短訊回覆本報表示：「He&rsquo;s okay，頭先已同記者講咗唔係入ICU，我係嚟逗利是。」<br />\n<br />\n賭王何鴻燊於09年，在四太梁安琪淺水灣道4號寓所跌倒，撞傷頭部，送院接受腦部手術，在港安及養和醫院養病半年才出院，之後由二、三及四房輪流照顧，近年賭王大部份時間留在養和休養，已絕跡公開場合。"},{"pid":"bb20dcc2efc8d9e72cb8b3e1a10a200a780b981e","tid":1013774,"uid":125731,"like":21,"dislike":1,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T15:13:08.000Z","msg":"好事近？？"},{"pid":"be6138fea009ea26e1841e6e08236ff28d043866","tid":1013774,"uid":1713,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T15:13:58.000Z","msg":"入廠維姐"},{"pid":"6623521972ff7f5b4445d15ae88d69b63d3d8021","tid":1013774,"uid":117837,"like":45,"dislike":1,"score":44,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T15:14:40.000Z","msg":"唔怪得超乜超物嗰啲扮晒乖仔上進唔靠父幹<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/pig2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e794d929b492c4acba0d5b30049f7148a8be22f6","tid":1013774,"uid":55533,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyT